Yacouba "Yac" Diori Hamani Magagi (bu onye amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke asaa n'ọnwa Septemba n'afọ 1997) bụ onye Nigerien na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbara klọb CD Castellón nke Spain na ndị otu mba Niger bọọlụ
Karịsịa onye na-agbachitere etiti, ọ pụkwara ịgba bọọlụ dịka onye na-egbochi bọọlụ ịbanye n'ime ebe  an na-enye goolu akpọrọ "Goal post" n'asụsụ bekee
A mụrụ ya na Niamey, Magagi malitere ọrụ ya na mba ofesi n'afọ 2016, ya na Club Internacional de la Amistad nke Spain na mpaghara
Na ụbọchị iri na abụọ nke ọnwa Septemba afọ ahụ, ọ kwagara SD Ponferradina, nke e kenyere na mbụ na nchekwa.
Magagi mere egwuregwu mbụ ya n'ụbọchị nke asaa ọnwa nke ise n'afọ 2017, malite na 0–0 n'ụlọ megide CD Tudelano na Segunda División B
A kwalitere ya na otu mbụ maka oge 2017–18, mana ọ na-apụtachaghị na mkpọsa nkwalite klọb ahụ.
Magagi mere egwuregwu izizi ya n'ụbọchị nke iri na iteghete nke ọnwa Ọktoba 2019, malite na 1–1 n'ụlọ megide CD Numancia
Na 20 Jenụwarị sochirinụ, ọ kwagara Getafe CF's reserves na mgbazinye ego maka oge fọdụrụnụ.

Mgbe ọ lọtara, Magagi gosipụtara obere oge tupu ọ banye na Primera División RFEF n'akụkụ CD Castellón na 22 Julaị 2021.
Na 25 Septemba Magagi nyere Castellón goolu mbụ ya, na-abịa na nkeji nke 89 megide UE Cornella iji jikọta egwuregwu ahụ 1–1.
Magagi mere egwuregwu mbụ ya na ndị otu mba Niger na 4 June 2016, malite na 2017 Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers 0–1 loss against Namibia
